column5: Heading out friday for a day on simcoe..i heard rumors that they have some huts out in front of jacksons point fro whities any truth to this?

I can't see anything that far over,but I'll be venturing off Innifil Park Friday morning(after I get a look today)....it's been covered and cold for 5 days,figure I'll try walking on it tomorrow.....reports to follow.....TC....Chuck...
